attributionInfo.brokerName: A Place in the Pines Realty LLC

data.description: With probably one of the greatest views in Midsouth, this golf front 4 bedroom home has more upgrades than you can imagine! The homeowners have been updating and upgrading since the home was built and purchased in 2018.  Starting outside with brand new zoysia sod, professional landscaping with a 10 zone irrigation system, downspouts with buried drain pipes, then into the garage with the belt driven garage openers and new insulated garage doors. They added a whole house generator and whole house water filtration system as well as a tankless Rinnai water heater that uses gas from the  500 gallon propane tank. Ceiling fans on the front porch will keep you cool in the summer time.  In the rear yard , there is a custom paver patio waiting for your most comfortable chairs. Inside you will find plantation shutters throughout, hardwood floors covering the first story, and a split floor plan including an office with built ins, stunning Carolina room with beautiful views and a 2 sided gas fireplace. The golf views continue from the primary suite which also features a stunning custom closet by Closets by Design. The open kitchen features a large center island, black stainless GE appliances including a gas cooktop and plenty of cabinet and pantry storage. The dining room features a custom coffered ceiling . The large bonus room upstairs could serve as a 4th bedroom. The home is wired for security and surround sound. Mid-Tal Membership required on this deed restricted property . For  transfer fee and information on dues info please call Donna at Midsouth Club .
